lookAll

public final java.util.List<ColoredChar> lookAll(Coord coord)
Returns everything visible from a given location. The top item is the last item in the list, with the actual tile being the first item in the list.

lookAll

public java.util.List<ColoredChar> lookAll(int x,
                                           int y)
Returns everything visible from a given location. The top item is the last item in the list, with the actual tile being the first item in the list. By default it only examines the tile, but should be overriden to take into account the tile's occupants and the proper draw order of the occupants.

passable
